{"an5.35:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 5.35 ","an5.35:0.2":"4. Sumanavagga ","an5.35:0.3":"Dananisamsasutta ","an5.35:1.1":"“Pancime, bhikkhave, dane anisamsa. ","an5.35:1.2":"Katame panca? ","an5.35:1.3":"Bahuno janassa piyo hoti manapo; ","an5.35:1.4":"santo sappurisa bhajanti; ","an5.35:1.5":"kalyano kittisaddo abbhuggacchati; ","an5.35:1.6":"gihidhamma anapagato hoti; ","an5.35:1.7":"kayassa bheda param marana sugatim saggam lokam upapajjati. ","an5.35:1.8":"Ime kho, bhikkhave, panca dane anisamsati. ","an5.35:2.1":"Dadamano piyo hoti, ","an5.35:2.2":"satam dhammam anukkamam; ","an5.35:2.3":"Santo nam sada bhajanti, ","an5.35:2.4":"sannata brahmacarayo. ","an5.35:3.1":"Te tassa dhammam desenti, ","an5.35:3.2":"Sabbadukkhapanudanam; ","an5.35:3.3":"Yam so dhammam idhannaya, ","an5.35:3.4":"Parinibbati anasavo”ti. ","an5.35:3.5":"Pancamam. "}